  "texts": [
    "One of the key strengths of our RAG model is its ability to leverage relevant information from PubMed literature to generate accurate and informative responses.",
    "However, we recognize the value of incorporating a wider range of data sources to further enhance the knowledge base and capabilities of our model.",
    "In future work, we aim to build a robust data aggregation framework that integrates multiple highquality data sources.",
    "In addition to PubMed, we plan to incorporate data from Mount Sinai's SAP HANA vector embeddings database, which contains a wealth of clinical and research data specific to multiple myeloma.",
    "Furthermore, we will explore integrating data from the Variant Interpretation for Cancer Consortium (VICC), the Clinical Interpretations of Variants in Cancer (CIVIC) database, and the Drug Gene Interaction Database (DGIdb)."
  ],
